3D Cloth customized website [React.js]

Working:
Home >> customizing cloth >> download

Tools:
Three.js: 
A powerful 3D graphic library for rendering and animating 3D models
React Three Fiber:
	It is a popular library for creating 3d graphics with 3js in react
Tailwind CSS:
	A popular utility first CSS styling framework.
Framer Motion:
	For animation in react.
**learn how to Lode >> create >> customize stunning 3D models, Geometries with various lights as well as understand the 3D world with the CAMERA & POSITION of an object in the space

**learn how to add custom color and file support generate and use images through Dali AI download the resulting t-shirt model image.

Installation:
	>> npm create vite@latest -- --template react client
		-create new react application inside react-app (folder)
	>>npm install three @react-three/fiber @react-three/drei maath valtio react-color framer-motion
		*three @react-three/fiber:
		-this is the react renderer for the 3js library
		*@react-three/drei:
		-contains useful add-ons for react three fiber
		*maath:
		-used for useful math helpers and mostly math thatâ€™s ment to be used with 3js.
		*valtio:
		-it is a new package that allows us to really easily manage react state
        *react-color:
        -it is a color picker
        *framer-motion:
        -used for cool animation


Setup TailwindCSS
    >>npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer
    >>npx tailwindcss init -p

